      "content": "Hey, I'm a personal trainer and I'm starting to work with a pretty diverse group of clients. As I'm putting together their programs, I wanted to ask your professional opinion on something: are there actually any significant biological differences in muscle composition, fiber types, or overall athletic potential between different racial groups that I should be taking into account for training efficiency?",
